# 采购链路主流程：依次执行以下请求，响应处理器会自动保存本流程产生的业务 ID。
### Procurement Flow 1/10 - Create Order
POST {{SkyRoc_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "customerId": "{{customerId}}",
  "quotationId": "{{quotationId}}",
  "wareId": "{{wareId}}",
  "orderDate": "2026-07-03 08:00:00",
  "receiveDate": "2026-07-05 08:00:00",
  "contactName": "张老师",
  "contactPhone": "13800005555",
  "deliveryAddress": "北京市朝阳区学校食堂",
  "remark": "订单到采购单主流程",
  "details": [
    {
      "goodsId": "{{goodsId}}",
      "goodsUnitId": "{{goodsUnitId}}",
      "quantity": 6,
      "fixedPrice": 4.5,
      "fixedGoodsUnitId": "{{goodsUnitId}}",
      "remark": "采购链路联调商品"
    }
  ]
}

> {%
    client.global.set("flowOrderId", response.body.data.id);
%}

